  "total_duration": 504.866,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 12.72,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象一个小镇明天要迎来一个很受欢迎的流行组合。火车什么时候到，年轻粉丝在哪里等，晚上在哪里演出，接下来几天有几场表演，大家都已经知道了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 13.07,
      "end": 30.758,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Greenwood Boys"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文可以说“绿林少年”。先别把它当成一节普通音乐课。它更像一张活动时间表：一个 pop-singer group 要巡演到小镇，粉丝兴奋，警察和工作人员要维持秩序。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 31.108,
      "end": 50.547,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里有两个背景要先看懂。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Greenwood Boys"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是故事里的流行演唱组合，类似 boy band；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Workers' Club"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是学校社团，也不是线上粉丝群，而是老式的本地工人俱乐部、社区活动场所，可以让大家聚会和看表演。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 50.897,
      "end": 74.06,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这一课的线索是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "tomorrow"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "到达，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "by train"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "坐火车来，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "at the station"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "车站迎接，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "tomorrow evening"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "晚上演出，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "for five days"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "待五天，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "keep order"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "维持秩序。把这张时间表看出来，课文就顺了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 74.41,
      "end": 96.53,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一帧，消息先传开："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Greenwood Boys are a group of pop singers."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "group"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里不是随便一群人，而是一个有成员、会演出的歌手组合。课文接着说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "At present, they are visiting all parts of the country."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "也就是他们目前正在全国各地巡回演出。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 96.879,
      "end": 112.983,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二帧，明天的到站安排来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They will be arriving here tomorrow."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他们明天会到这里。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "They will be coming by train and most of the young people in the town will be meeting them at the station."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这不是普通路过，是粉丝会去车站迎接。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 113.333,
      "end": 132.021,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三帧，晚上要去哪里？"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Tomorrow evening they will be singing at the Workers' Club."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Workers' Club"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以理解成工人俱乐部、社区活动场所，不是学校兴趣社团。这个小镇的演出不是大型体育馆，而是在本地俱乐部举行。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 132.371,
      "end": 157.042,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四帧，把后面几天和秩序问题接上："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Greenwood Boys will be staying for five days."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "During this time, they will give five performances."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "人多、粉丝兴奋，所以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "the police will have a difficult time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。他们不是抓坏人，而是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "trying to keep order"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，让大家安全、有序地排队和行动。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 157.392,
      "end": 160.472,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一课为什么不太像前几课的故事反转？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 160.822,
      "end": 166.207,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为它没有最后突然好笑的一下，更像在说接下来会发生什么？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 166.557,
      "end": 182.557,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。它像一张小镇演出日程表。先告诉你这个组合是谁，再说他们现在正在巡演，然后说明天到站、晚上演出、停留五天、五场表演，最后才说警察要维持秩序。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 182.907,
      "end": 189.122,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The Greenwood Boys"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是真实乐队吗？我要查资料吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 189.472,
      "end": 201.832,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不需要。把它当成故事里的流行演唱组合就可以。重点不是考乐队历史，而是看懂 popular event、excited crowd、clear schedule 和 order 这四件事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 202.182,
      "end": 206.084,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Workers' Club"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么要特别解释？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 206.434,
      "end": 216.694,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为中文孩子可能会以为 club 是学校社团，或者现在的线上粉丝俱乐部。这里更像一个本地社区场所，工人和居民可以聚会，也能办演出。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 217.044,
      "end": 222.33,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "警察"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will have a difficult time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，是不是说明会有犯罪？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 222.68,
      "end": 233.84,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是。这里是 crowd control，人多时要防止拥挤、堵路、乱跑，帮助大家排队和移动。语气要 lively and orderly，不是危险故事。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 234.19,
      "end": 242.919,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以这篇可以按时间来背：现在巡演，明天到，车站接，晚上唱，五天五场，警察维持秩序。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 243.269,
      "end": 252.189,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "完全对。你把时间表抓住，后面的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "will be doing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就不是一堆句型，而是一台放在未来的摄像机。"
        }
      ]
    },
